r size=1> I found that with every char I make, no matter what I end up going to qeynos hills.  You know why?  2 words, gnoll fangs.  These are the greatest.  You get so much xp its no even funny.  Now the best place to camp is by the entrance to BB, there are 2 other spawns very near, you will find them if you look.  You can easily kill all the gnoll with a pet.  I rarely lose, like only when there are 2 and one has a scythe or I am low in mana.  Your pet should be able to solo them almost.  And if things look grim simply run into BB.<br>
<br>
I have done this with at least 5 characters, one being a dark elf mage, and I never got killed by a wandering NPC(Holly Windstalker, Cros, etc).  I don't even think they are KOS, the only ppl this may not work for is Necro's and SK's.  But they just got to be careful.  Iksars have to be careful to, but I have seen an iksar do fine here.<br>
<br>
Anyway, if you get gnoll fangs, SAVE THEM.  Then take am to Captain Tillan in North qeynos, I think north.  Whatever one has the dock, bank and arena in it.  Anyway go to the arena and captain tillan is on the balcony, you can give him 4 fangs at a time.  I got almost entirely thru level 5 with these with my last char.  I topped off level 4 and was one bub short of 6.<br>
<br>
This is the best place to from 4 to 7 IMO.  After this head to Freeport and kills orcs and dervs.  But that's another forum, so I'll cya later.<br>
<br>
Zekx of Povar <br>
